and you'd have to stand on your own feet.

911
00:54:24,443 --> 00:54:28,436
Wow. I didn't see that coming.

912
00:54:28,847 --> 00:54:30,439
No. Well...

913
00:54:30,616 --> 00:54:32,516
...I have amazing insight.

914
00:54:32,684 --> 00:54:35,448
I would use it on myself,
only I don't have any problems.

915
00:54:36,889 --> 00:54:38,720
And I will tell you my other insight.

916
00:54:38,891 --> 00:54:42,725
I think you are way too talented
and gifted...

917
00:54:42,895 --> 00:54:47,195
